title: Dogfight (1991) River Phoenix (DVDrip)

With Lili Taylor

River Phoenix in an unusual part as a rather ordinary young man. The film was released 2 years before his tragic death.

Story is set in 1963, before some friends are shipped to Vietnam. They play a dirty game called 'Dogfight': All of them seek a woman for a party, and who finds the most ugly one, wins a prize. But games may turn around...

This is not my rip; I found it on another site using PirateBay's tracker, so I thought it should be represented here.

Widescreen 608x336, good stereo sound.
